  "gui.neoguanniao.bird_guide.entry.night_heron.title": "夜鹭",
  "gui.neoguanniao.bird_guide.entry.night_heron.subtitle": "水边夜班渔夫",
  "gui.neoguanniao.bird_guide.entry.night_heron.intro.title": "小记",
  "gui.neoguanniao.bird_guide.entry.night_heron.intro.body": "白天它像一截灰树枝，站在水边装作谁也没看见；天一暗，就开始沿岸上夜班。起飞时先用力扇几下，再借风滑出去，像是不慌不忙地把自己交给夜色。",
  "gui.neoguanniao.bird_guide.entry.sparrow.title": "麻雀",
  "gui.neoguanniao.bird_guide.entry.sparrow.subtitle": "屋檐下的小吵闹",
  "gui.neoguanniao.bird_guide.entry.sparrow.intro.title": "小记",
  "gui.neoguanniao.bird_guide.entry.sparrow.intro.body": "麻雀不稀奇，但少了它，村子会安静得不太像村子。它们蹦来蹦去，啄两口又抬头看你；面包屑一落地，先是一只装作路过，随后整群都想起自己刚好有事。",
  "gui.neoguanniao.bird_guide.entry.budgerigar.title": "虎皮鹦鹉",
  "gui.neoguanniao.bird_guide.entry.budgerigar.subtitle": "草地上的绿色吵闹云",
  "gui.neoguanniao.bird_guide.entry.budgerigar.intro.title": "小记",
  "gui.neoguanniao.bird_guide.entry.budgerigar.intro.body": "日出时它们像一阵绿色的风从树上炸开，白天低着头在草籽间忙忙碌碌；但只要音乐响起，总有几只会忍不住左右摇摆起来。",
  "gui.neoguanniao.bird_guide.entry.spotted_dove.title": "珠颈斑鸠",
  "gui.neoguanniao.bird_guide.entry.spotted_dove.subtitle": "农田林缘的低声天气哨",
  "gui.neoguanniao.bird_guide.entry.spotted_dove.intro.title": "小记",
  "gui.neoguanniao.bird_guide.entry.spotted_dove.intro.body": "它们大多数时候都在地上慢慢走，低头啄两口，又抬头咕一声。天色将变时，斑鸠的声音会忽然少下来，像是比玩家先听见了远处的雨。",
  "gui.neoguanniao.bird_guide.entry.pigeon.title": "鸽子",
  "gui.neoguanniao.bird_guide.entry.pigeon.subtitle": "屋檐和广场之间的熟面孔",
  "gui.neoguanniao.bird_guide.entry.pigeon.intro.title": "小记",
  "gui.neoguanniao.bird_guide.entry.pigeon.intro.body": "灰的、白的，混在人类建筑旁边也毫不见外。它们不急，低头走路，啄食，偶尔扑棱一下翅膀换个地方继续散步。",
